5 (6) There shall be no new applications for incentives filed under
6 this section after December 31, 2030. All complete applications filed on
7 or before December 31, 2030, shall be considered by the director and
8 approved if the location or locations and taxpayer qualify for benefits,
9 subject to the base authority limitations provided in section 77-6839.
10 Agreements may be executed with regard to complete applications filed on
11 or before December 31, 2030. All agreements pending, approved, or entered
12 into before such date shall continue in full force and effect.
13 (7) No incentives shall be given to a foreign adversarial company as
14 defined in section 77-3,114.
